				<wikidot:authorName>wishun</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1204404</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Reminds me of Killer Klowns From Outer Space; but with more creepy and less goofy, which makes it much, much better.</p> <p>In addition to the pre-mentioned impact of the phrase &quot;clown milk&quot;, the image of black cotton candy is incredibly simple and squicks me right the hell out.</p> <p>My only reservation is that it seems like there are an awful lot of sub-items. I had to pause and make sure I was keeping the various designations straight in my head. If the candy spinner is non-anomalous, why does it get a number?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
