					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>SCP-1921-A2 is any cotton candy produced from SCP-1921-A1 when SCP-1921-A3 is present inside the machine's reservoir.</p> </blockquote> <p>Aren't they worried about running out of the liquid?</p> <blockquote> <p>It was originally discovered underneath SCP-1921-A1 in a small tank labelled &quot;Clown Milk&quot;.</p> </blockquote> <p><em>Ewwwwwwwwwww!!!</em></p> 
